opened the eye, of the m$&s;t blind and unthink|ing,
and touched the mo&s;t callous and obdurate
heart. <HI>O fool! to think the man, who&s;e ample
mind mu&s;t gra&s;p whatever yonder &s;tars &s;urvey</HI>&mdash;
Prav, Mr. Pallet, what is your opinion of that
