<HEAD>CHAP. LII.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">Pallet conceives an hearty contempt for his fellow-traveller,
and attaches him&s;elf to Pickle, who,
neverthele&s;s, per&s;ecutes him with his mi&s;chievous
