of re&s;erve, which commonly happens be|tween
two per&s;ons, when their friend&s;hip is in
the wane.</P>
<P>Gauntlet at once divined the cau&s;e of the
other's di&s;plea&s;ure; and, in order to vindicate his
own character, after the fir&s;t compliments were
